For deployment edit the docker-compose.yml file and replace all `.localhost`
occourences with `.yourdomain.com`. This shall be automated with an ansible
template.

There are also a bunch of `TODO` where secrets are meant to be generated with
something akin to `openssl rand -base64 64`.

To get mattermost working with gitea SSO the hardcoded URLs for GitLab have to
be slightly changed as follows:
- "/oauth/authorize" -> "/login/oauth/authorize"
- "/oauth/token" -> "/login/oauth/access_token"
- "/api/v4" -> "/api/v1"
